name: Cubeman (ProTDC)
description:
in the videogame Cubeman you take the control  a cube called Cubeman as you platform your way through 10 levels and avoid all 2 enemies with 4 exciting difficulties: Easy, Normal, Fuck you and Speedrun.

Also my very first release of a videogame so i am not expecting it to go well

(and also no cubeman is NOT inspired by the hit game amogus please stop)
